{"word":"μάρναμαι","slug":"μάρναμαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μάρναμαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to fight, do battle</i>, <el>τινί</el> <i>with</i> or <i>against</i> another, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>ἐπί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>πρός τινα</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to quarrel, wrangle</i> with words, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>in <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b> <i>to contend, struggle, strive to one's uttermost</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}